{"tid":1118241,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"[畫鞋] 畫成片漸變色上對鞋","createTime":"2019-04-21T09:23:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T12:45:51.000Z","uid":202514,"like":49,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"91c794bbf92d15d80a6d2d16981bec78a318e61b","tid":1118241,"uid":202514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T09:23:17.000Z","msg":"又係我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次唔講畫技唔畫人<br />\n單純將對鞋改到漸變色<br />\n但就會講下好多巴打好有興趣嘅製作過程<br />\n<br />\n嚟個成品圖先 :<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uOumnYL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuOumnYL.png&h=94561ce7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fcYuwR7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfcYuwR7.png&h=069bfd90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好多時都唔記得影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n影返個鞋盒label先，本身單純一對全白鞋<br />\n貼好晒遮蓋膠紙係啲唔想上色嘅位就開得工<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bH5TYwG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbH5TYwG.png&h=1468925c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後就到整漸層嘅重點工具<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wWXGnZk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwWXGnZk.png&h=b3aff732&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就係噴槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴打睇到呢到唔好屌我住<br />\n就算無噴槍，用染料都ok<br />\n只係會無咁smooth，似水彩化染多啲<br />\n方法同平時畫水彩一樣，只係轉左用酒精開稀<br />\n<br />\n另外聽講觀塘有間鋪有得上去租噴槍用<br />\n但唔知用唔用得angelus paint<br />\n<br />\n今次呢隻漸變就用左以下呢四種色<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E3jNiBp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE3jNiBp.png&h=60178790&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一層，溝一滴下面嗰隻等佢無咁鮮<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yCoVsuM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyCoVsuM.png&h=b3428685&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第二層，直接用<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H3uYqgt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH3uYqgt.png&h=56f95c04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n都係直接用嘅第三層<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NG2WbWv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNG2WbWv.png&h=6276899d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n溝左少少Caramel等佢無咁深<br />\n<br />\n過程無影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但重點有三個<br />\n第一，上嘅次序淺色到深色會好啲<br />\n因為噴多左都易救啲，可以用深色遮返佢<br />\n第二，拎遠啲噴，大約10-15cm距離<br />\n一嚟避免太多顏料太厚<br />\n二嚟噴得廣左個漸層會漸變得靚啲<br />\n第三，唔好心急<br />\n唔好因為上得太淺就隊埋去/㩒到最盡<br />\n咁會太過實色，而且亦會搞到層顏料太厚會易甩左<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XMZdYED.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXMZdYED.png&h=8c42e8b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n得一開始有影，改到忘我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/21/171440_8ffbccabf09635d6ca9d680780c13d9b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F21%2F171440_8ffbccabf09635d6ca9d680780c13d9b.png&h=633b5a2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁噴完拆膠紙之後其實都仲有嘢做<br />\n就係執漏，有啲位膠紙突左少少出嚟就上返好佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DHXfsAE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDHXfsAE.png&h=a0441335&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gobsiHx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgobsiHx.png&h=7c1454a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後上層finisher就搞掂<br />\n但呢對仲有啲細節想加所以我就未上住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n照舊有啲咩問題答到嘅都會盡答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b8e692ec214198bf1ea84213eadabf2300f717f","tid":1118241,"uid":202514,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T09:27:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">覺得正嘅支持下小弟，<br />\nfollow返個ig :<br />\nyauyau_jy</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/yauyau_jy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fyauyau_jy&d=CcUT5H46krin9iWjsTG5RGhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=48dface2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.instagram.com/yauyau_jy</a>"},{"pid":"effda73cd56ce6934930340b18d9bdc3fb40da68","tid":1118241,"uid":52793,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T09:30:47.000Z","msg":"落雨係咪變返白"},{"pid":"bfe7ba4a37d357c949a4777623e27f70499c9f4f","tid":1118241,"uid":202514,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"effda73cd56ce6934930340b18d9bdc3fb40da68","tid":1118241,"uid":52793,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T09:30:47.000Z","msg":"落雨係咪變返白"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T09:34:07.000Z","msg":"塑膠彩嚟<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GdFs3ek.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGdFs3ek.png&h=623236e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本身就防水，上層glazer係保護佢唔好咁易花"},{"pid":"f9b45659c35a20b070f8ad634d89d8b2589d596e","tid":1118241,"uid":202514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T09:53:57.000Z","msg":"Up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6c05dc5d3e6b6b1e75ae2477e5dd59f402c4b29","tid":1118241,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T10:24:58.000Z","msg":"玩左幾耐？<br />\n幾有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69797782ca84c747a76801bc99cc6be177385a9d","tid":1118241,"uid":202514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6c05dc5d3e6b6b1e75ae2477e5dd59f402c4b29","tid":1118241,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T10:24:58.000Z","msg":"玩左幾耐？<br />\n幾有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T10:27:50.000Z","msg":"噴個過程連埋換色洗噴槍大概一個鐘多啲就搞掂<br />\n貼膠紙反而搞仲耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8e1ffb5c42861514b41b77527ca73db532d29f7","tid":1118241,"uid":202514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T11:39:11.000Z","msg":"UPUP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7964d2946f6c704c1b93f8fe0aadc61e3373098d","tid":1118241,"uid":203495,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T12:45:12.000Z","msg":"我都霖住自己整對Air force 但係畫畫好差"},{"pid":"1614ff1e5bf8869b4325c7dade8341bb17a89c05","tid":1118241,"uid":202514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7964d2946f6c704c1b93f8fe0aadc61e3373098d","tid":1118241,"uid":203495,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T12:45:12.000Z","msg":"我都霖住自己整對Air force 但係畫畫好差"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T13:50:09.000Z","msg":"可以試下係個勾到畫下花紋先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0b3312ab425a453854a130d8daba13fe3b996be","tid":1118241,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfe7ba4a37d357c949a4777623e27f70499c9f4f","tid":1118241,"uid":202514,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"effda73cd56ce6934930340b18d9bdc3fb40da68","tid":1118241,"uid":52793,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T09:30:47.000Z","msg":"落雨係咪變返白"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T09:34:07.000Z","msg":"塑膠彩嚟<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GdFs3ek.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGdFs3ek.png&h=623236e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本身就防水，上層glazer係保護佢唔好咁易花"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T14:14:29.000Z","msg":"著落會唔會好焗唔透氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c4cf7cf4cd3738b0e4e2a5a3d1ebcf5c5b5a9bb","tid":1118241,"uid":202514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0b3312ab425a453854a130d8daba13fe3b996be","tid":1118241